- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper mentions a new type of contract based on behavioral patterns. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is another possibility as the paper mentions the use of formal verification techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a less likely possibility as the paper mentions the use of statistical model checking, which is a subfield of AI, but the focus of the paper is on SoS and not AI.
